
delete-key-pair
***************


DESCRIPTION
===========

The delete-key-pair operation deletes a key pair.


SYNOPSIS
========

   aws ec2 delete-key-pair
     --key-name <value>


REQUIRED PARAMETERS
===================

"--key-name"  (string)
   The name of the Amazon EC2 key pair to delete.


OPTIONAL PARAMETERS
===================

None
